-- encoded proofs of  TreeEq (cor a_i) (cor b_i) = cor (TreeEq a_i b_i)
-- at sub-pairs to fold the substituted RHS into  cor (TreeEq ... ) .
-- Those are cross-IH proofs; calling them "encoded substitutions"
-- doesn't make them appear from nowhere.  The substitution operation
-- replaces variables with terms, not  TreeEq  applications with their
-- cor-images.
--
-- Until a working NN bridge is built using parEncRuleInst alone, treat
